body_html: Follow-up question: is it possible to mmap a quantized graph? I've been trying and encountering the same issue that @eaigner was encountering above. Without quantization, my graph is huge but runs into memory issues on IOS. With quantization, it's small and I think it will work but I cannot mmap now.
